title: Jury will decide amount Giuliani will pay to 2 Georgia election workers for defamation
description: How much should it cost to defame two innocent citizens in the service of a dangerous fallacy that sought to undermine a U.S. presidential election?

title: Scientists have found the mostly intact skull of a giant, deadly sea reptile
description: The pliosaur, which existed millions of years ago, would chomp down with its 130 teeth in a bite far stronger than a crocodile's and had a third eye for locating prey.

title: High Court, in declining to weigh conversion therapy ban, allows law to stand
description: In doing so, the court left standing a lower court decision that upheld the state's ban on a therapy that the American Medical Association says "is not based on medical and scientific evidence."
